different scenarios

00:06:32.500 --> 00:06:35.320
we thought we were going
to experience inside Gaza.

00:06:35.320 --> 00:06:37.840
During the night,
we were waiting.

00:06:37.840 --> 00:06:41.160
We were waiting for the
final call to invade Gaza.

00:06:41.160 --> 00:06:42.910
Each night we came
prepared with our gear,

00:06:42.910 --> 00:06:47.920
with our vests, grenades,
magazines, rifles,

00:06:47.920 --> 00:06:49.463
