that's going to be

00:06:53.255 --> 00:06:54.800
a disrespect to
your intelligence.

00:06:54.800 --> 00:06:56.830
Yes, we did made sure
we have enough candies

00:06:56.830 --> 00:06:58.120
for the rough times.

00:06:58.120 --> 00:07:01.930
It's essential sometimes
